  <brief_title>The Role of Hypertonic Dextrose Spray as Endoscopic Topical Hemostatic Agent for Acute Non-Variceal Upper GI Bleeding</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Hypertonic Dextrose Spray as Endoscopic Topical Hemostatic Agent for Acute Non-Variceal Upper Gastrointestinal Bleeding: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
