      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Patients with acute non-variceal upper gastrointestinal bleeding caused by peptic or&#xD;
             duodenal ulcer, polyps, tumors or malignancy&#xD;
&#xD;
